
build the hardware

install an img to cf card and insert card in system

hook hardware up to existing audio infra (PA or whatnot)

boot the system

telnet to the system

set password with passwd

hack /etc/mpdas for audioscrobbling

hack /etc/mpd.conf if you want a password based mpd setup

change the password in /etc/pymodtouchgui based on needs

install additional clients on you mobe or elsewhere

hand out infos and display qr codes so other may get clients

have fun!
